title: Scorpio girl
description: low poly model for your projects
longDescription: In the project, there are 4 assembly options for the model, 2 of them have a face morph and the model is modular. The model is equipped with an epic skeleton with additional bones for the tail and hair, and 3 textures were also made for the model
